The paper discusses a machine learning method that focuses on improving performance in healthcare applications where there may be limited training data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of transfer learning, which is a common technique in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) applications. The paper also mentions the use of probabilistic weighting, which is a technique commonly used in Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Neural Networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, and cs.NE.
